<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪和尼娜在荡秋千。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们是几个星期前在儿童中心认识的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪喜欢尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“秋天是我最喜欢的季节。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，我也喜欢秋天。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们！来拿你们的坐垫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们很快就要用到了！” 雪莉老师喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿童中心的活动时间到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道今天我们要做什么。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿着一个棕色的纸袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她穿着靴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去树林里了！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家跟着雪莉老师走进了一条小路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小路通往树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到了。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们今天的露营地。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在这里做什么？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以随便放坐垫吗？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。” 雪莉老师回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把纸袋的东西倒到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天，我们要用火、棉花糖、巧克力和全麦饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有谁可以猜到我们要做什么吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全麦饼干三明治！” 波比大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的最爱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定很好吃！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们家去露营的时候就会做全麦饼干三明治。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是全麦饼干三明治？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是全麦饼干三明治？” 尼娜惊讶地又问了一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，你今天要尝到好吃的啦！” 雪莉老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要先生火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们每个人找一根细细长长的树枝，然后清理一下。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，这根不错！” 尼娜边说边清理一根长树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们用这个烤棉花糖。” 贾森告诉莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，把棉花糖插在树枝上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像这样。” 波比做给莉琪看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪举起树枝。“好了。现在呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们来烤棉花糖吧！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心地把树枝放在火的上方，而不是火里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢黏糊糊的棉花糖。那样最好吃。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“才不是呢。烤焦、脆皮的才最好吃。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪尖叫起来。“雪莉老师！我的棉花糖着火了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像吹生日蜡烛一样吹灭它就可以了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起莉琪的树枝，把火吹灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是全麦饼干三明治吗？” 莉琪拿着烤焦的棉花糖问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还不是。现在我们要拿两片全麦饼干。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一块巧克力。” 贾森补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把巧克力放在一片全麦饼干上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>再把棉花糖放在巧克力上。” 波比做给她看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把另外一片全麦饼干放在上面，像三明治一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后压一下。” 尼娜压了压自己的三明治。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>融化的巧克力流了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪和尼娜哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全麦饼干三明治真好吃！” 莉琪擦了擦嘴上的棉花糖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吃吧？正适合在秋天吃。” 雪莉老师笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看了看四周，然后她看了看自己的新朋友尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师说得对。一切都太完美了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>